<li>Sending you strength and love during this incredibly difficult time.  Your family is in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
<li>Words cannot express the sorrow I feel for your family's loss.  Please know that I am here for you.</li>
<li>May the love and support of those around you help ease your pain during this time of grief.</li>
<li>Holding your family in my heart as you navigate this difficult journey.</li>
