<li>I am so sorry for your loss. Your family is in my thoughts and prayers.</li>
<li>Your loved one will be deeply missed, but their memory will live on forever.</li>
<li>May the beautiful memories of your loved one bring you solace.</li>
<li>Sending love and strength to your family during this time of sorrow.</li>
